Follow the trail of lights in Australia’s outback
Embark on a journey filled with enchantment in the outback of Australia's Northern Territory. This trail leads you to vibrant art installations, natural wonders and light festivals that celebrate the rich heritage of indigenous communities. It weaves in unforgettable dining and camping experiences beneath celestial night skies. It also winds through magical locations where the interplay of light and nature casts spellbinding displays. Within Australia's vast and untamed wilderness, let the lights be your guide to an awe-inspiring adventure.
